gnome-power-manager: gnome-power-manager (GNOME Power Manager)
gnome-power-manager: 
gnome-power-manager: GNOME Power Manager is a session daemon for the GNOME Desktop environment 
gnome-power-manager: that makes it easy to manage your laptop or desktop system's power 
gnome-power-manager: usage.  It requires HAL, and supports suspending, hibernating, power 
gnome-power-manager: notifications, cpu frequencies, hard drive spin-down, and display 
gnome-power-manager: dimming. 
